'''Louw Venter''' (yavutse ku ya 16 Kanama 1975), ni Umukinnyi wa firime wo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika yepfo]] akaba n'umukinnyi wa firime. <ref>https://halal.amsterdam/people/louw-venter/</ref> ''Azwi cyane mubuyobozi'' bwe no kwandika muri firime zizwi cyane ''Igiti'', Konfetti na ''Swartwater'' .

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 16 Kanama 1975 i Cape Town, muri Afurika y'Epfo.

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2001, yakinnye bwa mbere muri firime na ''Final Solution'' aho yagize uruhare ruto nk 'umunyamuryango wa Paramilitary. Mu 2002, yakinnye 'Marco' muri filime yo mu Butaliyani ''The Piano Player'' iyobowe na Jean-Pierre Roux. Mu 2003, yakinnye muri firime ebyiri: ''Adrenaline'' na ''Citizen Verdict'' .

Usibye gukina, ni n'umwanditsi w'inyandiko wanditse filime yatsindiye ibihembo bya ''Konfetti'' yayobowe na Zaheer Goodman-Bhyat . Usibye ibyo, yari umwanditsi wa ''serivise za tereviziyo: Rugby Motors'' na ''Vinkel & Koljander'' . Muri 2015, yerekanwe bwa mbere na firime ngufi ''Leemte'' . Nyuma yo gutsinda kwa firime, yakoze televiziyo ''Vinkel & Koljander'' muri 2016. Muri 2016, yamenyekanye cyane muri firime  ''Kalushi: The Story of Solomon Mahlangu'',, yari ishingiye ku nkuru y'impamo. Muri filime, yakinnye uruhare rwa 'Van Heerden'. Filime yagenze neza kandi itangwa mubirori byinshi bya firime.

Venter yakoze kandi urwenya hamwe na mugenzi we wo gusetsa muri Afurika yepfo Rob Van Vuuren. Bombi bagaragaye nk'abantu bavugwa Corne (Venter) na Twakkie (Van Vuuren) murukurikirane rwa videwo ya YouTube <ref>https://www.youtube.com/user/CorneTwakkie/</ref> na gahunda yitwa ''The Amazing Show'' . Venter yakinnye kandi murumuna wa Van Vuuren muri comedi ya ''Van der Merwe'' muri 2017.

Muri 2020, yayoboye kandi yandika filime ye ya mbere yitwa ''Stam'' yasohotse kuri BoxOffice ya DStv mu Kwakira. <ref>https://springsadvertiser.co.za/248487/stam-is-a-uniquely-afrikaans-film-new-louw-venter-film-shows-we-are-all-connected/</ref> Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku isi yose mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Durban muri Nzeri 2020. Yerekanwe kandi muri 18 ya Tofifest International Film Festival 2020 muri Polonye. <ref>https://newsofafrica.org/south-african-film-stam-chosen-to-compete-in-the-18th-annual-film-festival.html</ref> <ref>https://www.iol.co.za/entertainment/movies/news/sa-film-stam-chosen-to-compete-in-polish-film-festival-ea0cb7f5-f8d7-4787-a712-b6619caa79e6</ref> <ref>https://www.thesouthafrican.com/lifestyle/sa-tv-film/stam-south-african-film-tofifest/</ref> Iyi filime yatsindiye igihembo cyiza cya Afurika yepfo mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Durban 2020 (DIFF). <ref>https://www.bizcommunity.com/Article/196/482/208511.html</ref> <ref>http://www.gautengfilm.org.za/2019-news-2/283-september/1944-louw-venter-s-stam-the-tree-wins-best-sa-film-at-diff</ref>

